snippet.title: JuVentures - Official Steam Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Our official Steam Early Access launch Trailer from 5. Jan. 2018

The JuVentures is a pure hidden object game with lovely detailed artwork hand-drawn by JujiBla. Accompany our heroes Nita and Snek on their journey through the land, explore strange places and discover magical things.

Website: http://juventures.click/
Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/769420/JuVentures/
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/jujibla
Twitter: https://twitter.com/JujiBla

Game Version: 0.3.5
